author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Antec Flux Pro case on Amazon https://geni.us/CaPv
This is the ultimate showdown: The AMD RX 9070 XT as found in the Yeston RX 9070 XT Sakura Sugar Atlantis OC "Waifu" GPU vs. the PowerColor RX 9070 XT Red Devil video card. In this graphics card comparison and benchmark, we first test the marketing claims against each other, then we bring them to battle in our hemi-anechoic chamber for acoustics, our thermal test room for GPU and VRAM temperature testing, and even through some games we hand-selected for their biases towards waifus or evil beings.

Watch our Yeston RX 9070 XT Waifu standalone review and tear down here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bs1O21ibuKM

The best way to support our work is through our store: https://store.gamersnexus.net/
